query:
/*+  */ select count(*)
from question AS q
inner join tag_question AS tq
on tq.question_id = q.id AND q.score >= 0 AND q.score <= 0
inner join site AS s
on tq.site_id = s.site_id AND q.site_id = s.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('stackoverflow')
inner join tag AS t
on tq.tag_id = t.id AND t.site_id = s.site_id AND t.name IN ('amazon-dynamodb',
'backbone.js',
'browser',
'format',
'iterator',
'logging',
'momentjs',
'mysql-workbench',
'reference',
'sap',
'ssl-certificate',
'width',
'wildfly',
'winforms',
'youtube');
